III. Potential Interests and Participants



The Commission has identified the following interests as those most likely to be significantly affected by the proposed
rules:

(a) Developers, manufacturers, and licensees of Local Multipoint Distribution Service;

(b) Pending mobile-satellite applicants in the 1610-1625.5/2483.5-2500 MHz band filing by the June
2, 1991 cutoff date for these applications;

(c) Fixed-satellite service applicants and service providers.

